{"baseRefName":"main","body":"The most significant changes include dependency version upgrades and dependency additions in the Maven configuration, as well as refactoring test method names for better clarity and consistency. \r\n\r\nDependency and build configuration updates:\r\n\r\n* Upgraded `spring-boot-starter-parent` version from 4.0.1 to 4.0.3, and updated versions for `webjars-locator` and `checkstyle` to newer releases in `pom.xml`. \r\n* Added `spring-boot-starter-restclient` as a test dependency in `pom.xml`.\r\n* Moved the `<licenses>` section in `pom.xml` to the end of the file for improved organization. \r\n\r\nTest code refactoring:\r\n\r\n* Renamed test methods throughout the test classes to follow a more descriptive and consistent naming convention, improving readability and maintainability. For example, methods like `testFindAll()` are now `findAll()`. \r\n\r\nMinor code cleanups are also present.","comments":[{"id":"IC_kwDOAHK23s7wmW5i","author":{"login":"patbaumgartner"},"authorAssociation":"CONTRIBUTOR","body":"hi @dsyer - I had just another round of updates for the Pet Clinic. Can you please merge? TIA ","createdAt":"2026-03-11T05:34:27Z","includesCreatedEdit":false,"isMinimized":false,"minimizedReason":"","reactionGroups":[],"url":"https://github.com/spring-projects/spring-petclinic/pull/2279#issuecomment-4036587106","viewerDidAuthor":false}],"files":[{"path":"README.md","additions":2,"deletions":2},{"path":"build.gradle","additions":11,"deletions":6},{"path":"docker-compose.yml","additions":2,"deletions":2},{"path":"k8s/db.yml","additions":1,"deletions":1},{"path":"pom.xml","additions":19,"deletions":10},{"path":"src/main/java/org/springframework/samples/petclinic/model/NamedEntity.java","additions":1,"deletions":1},{"path":"src/main/java/org/springframework/samples/petclinic/owner/PetController.java","additions":2,"deletions":1},{"path":"src/main/java/org/springframework/samples/petclinic/owner/PetTypeFormatter.java","additions":1,"deletions"